          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-662-0252-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-662-0252-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-662-0252-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-662-0252-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">P</hi>OOR Ladies! though their Bus'ness be to play,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-0252-line-2" n="2">'Tis hard they must be busy Night and Day:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-0252-line-3" n="3">Why should they want the Privilege of Men,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-0252-line-4" n="4">To take some small Diversions now and then?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-0252-line-5" n="5">Had Women been the Makers of our Laws;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-0252-line-6" n="6">(And why they were not, I can see no Cause;)</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-0252-line-7" n="7">The Men should slave at Cards from Morn to Night;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-662-0252-line-8" n="8">And Female Pleasures be to read and write.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
